  {
    "user": "UCUSW7WVD",
    "type": "message",
    "ts": "1736374107.199829",
    "client_msg_id": "a062d73a-f164-4a42-9743-fef5ec65b569",
    "text": "I remember this one! I kinda didn't feel like it disagreed with me much even though I care about people learning programming. Because I think of programming as \"using the best modeling tools we've managed to come up with so far.\"\n\nImagine you lived in Ancient Rome. Imagine saying it wasn't worth learning numbers because the Roman numeral system sucks, and you're just sure there's something new called \"positional notation\" about to launch _real soon now._\n\nSo there's no \"the\" new literacy. There are only occasional \"a\" new literacies. And they're few enough and far enough apart that we shouldn't ignore any of them.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1736371579.847269",
    "parent_user_id": "U08294YLWJH",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "MhXu+",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I remember this one! I kinda didn't feel like it disagreed with me much even though I care about people learning programming. Because I think of programming as \"using the best modeling tools we've managed to come up with so far.\"\n\nImagine you lived in Ancient Rome. Imagine saying it wasn't worth learning numbers because the Roman numeral system sucks, and you're just sure there's something new called \"positional notation\" about to launch "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "real soon now.",
                "style": {
                  "italic": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nSo there's no \"the\" new literacy. There are only occasional \"a\" new literacies. And they're few enough and far enough apart that we shouldn't ignore any of them."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "channel_name": "linking-together",
    "channel_id": "C5U3SEW6A"
  },
