            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The problem with the paper metaphor is kind of overblown. Nowdays there are quite a few other metaphors (infinity canvas, infinity scroll, trees, graphs, links..). Also webapps are not really websites anymore (for better or worse). We do have to remember that many computer users are *very* limited in their ability."
